  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocai_jiaocai_en_91_1",
    "text": "In addition, we define that \"an employee fits a job\" if and only if the employee has all skills that are needed by the job.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1483272873841193,
      0.1413709562491093,
      0.852881902458686,
      0.17557360695453897
    ],
    "page": "jiaocai_jiaocai_en_91",
    "order": 2
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocai_jiaocai_en_91_2",
    "text": "Please write relational algebra expressions for the following queries.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.14913341394598953,
      0.18127404873877725,
      0.7077791213220476,
      0.1989454182699159
    ],
    "page": "jiaocai_jiaocai_en_91",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocai_jiaocai_en_91_3",
    "text": "1) Find the name of female employees who have at least one skill needed by the “DEV\"job. 2) Find the names of employees who fit the \"DEV\" job.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.14913341394598953,
      0.2046458600541542,
      0.8125755743651754,
      0.26279036625338464
    ],
    "page": "jiaocai_jiaocai_en_91",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocai_jiaocai_en_91_4",
    "text": "2. SQL Query (20 points, 5 points each)",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.14913341394598953,
      0.2696308963944706,
      0.5554212011285772,
      0.2890123984608807
    ],
    "page": "jiaocai_jiaocai_en_91",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocai_jiaocai_en_91_5",
    "text": "Consider the relational schemas given in problem 1, please write SQL statements to meet the following requests.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1483272873841193,
      0.294712840245119,
      0.8359532446594116,
      0.32834544677212485
    ],
    "page": "jiaocai_jiaocai_en_91",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocai_jiaocai_en_91_6",
    "text": "1) Find the employees who have not any skills. 2) Find the jobs that need at least\"Java\" and \"C++\"skills. 3) Find the names of employees who have the maximum number of skills among all employees. 4) Find the employees who fit both the \"DEV\" and \"UAT\" jobs.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1483272873841193,
      0.33461593273478696,
      0.845626763401854,
      0.4395040615647713
    ],
    "page": "jiaocai_jiaocai_en_91",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocai_jiaocai_en_91_7",
    "text": "3. Embedded SQL (10 points)",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
